import React from 'react';
import { View, Text, Image, TouchableOpacity, ScrollView } from 'react-native';

import css from "./Style"
import global from "../Global/Style"

export default function Funcionario({navigation}){
    return(
        <View style={global.body}>
            <Image style={css.image} source={require("../assets/logo.png")}/>
            <View style={css.scrollView}>
                <ScrollView>
                    <TouchableOpacity style={css.card} onPress={() => {navigation.navigate("MeuPerfil")}}>
                        <Text style={css.title}>Meu perfil</Text>
                    </TouchableOpacity>
                    <TouchableOpacity style={css.card} onPress={() => {navigation.navigate("ListarFuncionario")}}>
                        <Text style={css.title}>Listar funcion√°rios</Text>
                    </TouchableOpacity>
                    <TouchableOpacity style={css.card} onPress={() => {navigation.navigate("CadastrarFuncionario")}}>
                        <Text style={css.title}>Cadastrar</Text>
                    </TouchableOpacity>
                </ScrollView>
            </View>
        </View>
    )
}
